item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - BRITNEY SPEARS updated DOLBY ATMOS albums on AM?
item.description:
I read that today more Britney albums are showing up in Dolby Atmos on Apple Music (Glory, Britney Jean, In the Zone, BOMT). And others (Blackout, Circus, FF) have been for a while. Maybe someone could rip the newly updated ones? And this thread may also serve as a way to post all of Brit’s albums in DA so far?
Thanks!!!
item.author: Apocodaus11
